__package__.yml.rawContents:
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    createAnimal:
      path: /animal
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        body: Animal
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: Animal
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request:
            breed: breed
            animalType: dog
          response:
            body:
              breed: breed
              barkVolume: 1.1
              animalType: dog
    createShape:
      path: /shape
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        body: Shape
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: Shape
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request:
            shapeType: shapeType
            radius: 1.1
          response:
            body:
              shapeType: shapeType
              radius: 1.1
    createPayment:
      path: /payment
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        body: Payment
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: Payment
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request:
            cardNumber: cardNumber
            paymentMethod: credit_card
          response:
            body:
              cardNumber: cardNumber
              expiryDate: expiryDate
              cvv: cvv
              paymentMethod: credit_card
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml
types:
  Dog:
    properties:
      breed: string
      barkVolume: optional<double>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Cat:
    properties:
      color: optional<string>
      indoor: optional<boolean>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Bird:
    properties:
      wingspan: optional<double>
      canFly: boolean
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Animal:
    discriminant: animalType
    base-properties: {}
    union:
      dog: Dog
      cat: Cat
      bird: Bird
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Circle:
    properties:
      shapeType: string
      radius: double
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Square:
    properties:
      shapeType: string
      sideLength: double
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Shape:
    discriminated: false
    union:
      - Circle
      - Square
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  CreditCardPayment:
    properties:
      cardNumber: string
      expiryDate: optional<string>
      cvv: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  BankTransferPayment:
    properties:
      accountNumber: string
      routingNumber: optional<string>
      bankName: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  CryptoPaymentCurrency:
    enum:
      - BTC
      - ETH
      - USDT
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  CryptoPayment:
    properties:
      walletAddress: string
      currency: CryptoPaymentCurrency
      network: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Payment:
    discriminant: paymentMethod
    base-properties: {}
    union:
      credit_card: CreditCardPayment
      bank_transfer: BankTransferPayment
      crypto: CryptoPayment
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: Discriminator Unions Edge Cases
